...then get inside with your sisters.

8
00:03:20,967 --> 00:03:22,025
拿去，爸爸
(SPEAKlNG FRENCH)
Ready, Papa.

9
00:03:32,378 --> 00:03:33,436
谢谢你，乖女儿...
(SPEAKlNG FRENCH)
Thank you, my darling...

10
00:03:34,147 --> 00:03:35,774
...现在进去陪你姐姐
